              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Boson model calculations.",
                " The lifetimes on low-lying states in Sm-150 were",
                " obtained using the (n,gamma) reaction and are given in",
                " table 3. The new range of values for 2(+)2-state is",
                " in agreement with the previous measurement, whereas",
                " the measured lifetime for 2(+)3-state-(0.625-1.156 ps)",
                " is a factor of 2-3 smaller than the literature value."
              ]
            }
          ],
